metadata.name: "Journey to The Ethera"
metadata.description:
***It is the story of a fictional world called "Ethera" as a fantasy world. Where explorers go in search of the lost treasure "Ethereum" and for the animal of this world I use the Arowana (known as Dragon fish) and goldfish to represent wealth and abundance.***

*2000x2923 pixels*
